OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,FResidents in Bridgend could face a
OL,7,Fbill of up to #7,000 each as a result
OL,8,Fof a leaking pipe in their gardens.
OL,10,FThe dispute has been ongoing for two
OL,11,Fyears, as residents say they are not
OL,12,Freceiving sufficient evidence of the
OL,13,Fleak.
OL,15,FThe five houses affected in
OL,16,FPontycymer, Bridgend, say that Dwr
OL,17,FCymru Welsh Water told them the
OL,18,Frepairs must be self-funded by the end
OL,19,Fof July 2026, or they could be taken
OL,20,Fto court.
OL,26,@xD@as{
