PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784546293
OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,FThey have made claims that the company
OL,7,Fis using "bullying tactics".
OL,9,FEddie Wood, who has lived at the house
OL,10,Ffor over three-decades, says he has
OL,11,Fhad sleepless nights since he received
OL,12,Fthe first letter about the pipe.
OL,14,FHe said: "I worry about it when I'm in
OL,15,Fbed at night and even first thing in
OL,16,Fthe morning. I'm 86 now so I don't
OL,17,Fhave the money coming in that I used
OL,18,Fto and it can feel quite isolating
OL,19,Fhaving to fight such a big
OL,20,Forganisation."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
