CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784546293
OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,FAnother resident, Nerys Walters, said
OL,7,Fthe dispute had brought her massive
OL,8,Famounts of stress over the last two
OL,9,Fyears with prosecution looming if they
OL,10,Fdon't pay for the works they estimate
OL,11,Fcould cost over #7,000 each.
OL,13,FThis would go towards replacing the
OL,14,Frear water pipe in their back gardens
OL,15,Fwith a new pipe at the front of the
OL,16,Fterraced row, along with connecting it
OL,17,Fto each house individually.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
