CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784546293
OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Local Democracy
OL,7,Freporting Service, Nerys said while
OL,8,Fthey initially thought they could get
OL,9,Fthese repairs made through their
OL,10,Finsurance, with no evidence of the
OL,11,Fleak being provided, insurers have
OL,12,Fsaid they would not pay out.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
