PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784546293
OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,FNerys said: "It's been a nightmare
OL,7,Fsituation for us that has really
OL,8,Fcaused us all a lot of stress. Welsh
OL,9,FWater have said they would pay for a
OL,10,Fnew line that runs parallel to the
OL,11,Ffront of property, but we would then
OL,12,Fhave to fund the cost of it coming in
OL,13,Ffrom the gate, and through the house
OL,14,Fto our rear stop-cock.
OL,16,F"We spoke to numerous contractors who
OL,17,Fquoted us at more than a thousand
OL,18,Fpounds a metre for this work which we
OL,19,Fdon't have spare.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784546293
OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,F"Our insurance company said they would
OL,7,Fpay but first they needed a report
OL,8,Ffrom Welsh Water with evidence of
OL,9,Fwhere the leak is coming from and
OL,10,Fconfirming that we are responsible for
OL,11,Fit.
OL,13,F"This has been going on for about year
OL,14,Fand a half now and we've been asking
OL,15,Ffor that evidence ever since, but have
OL,16,Fbeen given nothing.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784546293
OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,F"No evidence of the leak, and no
OL,7,Freason as to why they adopted other
OL,8,Fpipes in the street but not ours. All
OL,9,Fthe while the deadline they have given
OL,10,Fruns down. It's been very difficult
OL,11,Fand we just want to get it sorted."
OL,13,FA local councillor in the area, Martyn
OL,14,FJones, says the residents were being
OL,15,Fforced to pay the repair costs out of
OL,16,Ftheir pocket, for an issue they were
OL,17,Finitially 'oblivious' to.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
