FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784546293
OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,FCllr Jones says he has met with an
OL,7,Fengineer at Welsh Water for the
OL,8,Fresidents, but he has not seen any
OL,9,Fevidence that any of of the residents
OL,10,Fare liable for the issue.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Welsh Water says
OL,13,Fthe company has been working alongside
OL,14,Fthe residents "who have a leak on a
OL,15,Fprivate, shared pipe to their
OL,16,Fproperties".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
