CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784546293
OL,3,CResidents say they face #7,000 or
OL,4,Ccourt for leaking pipe in garden
OL,6,FThey added: "The pipe is not owned or
OL,7,Fmanaged by Dwr Cymru Welsh Water and
OL,8,Fis the responsibility of the property
OL,9,Fowners. However, to support the
OL,10,Fresidents we have offered a free
OL,11,Fconnection to our main if each
OL,12,Fproperty connects individually.
OL,14,F"We appreciate this will be an
OL,15,Finconvenience for customers so we have
OL,16,Falso offered a contribution towards
OL,17,Fthe cost of the required work to get a
OL,18,Fpipe from the properties to the main."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/9
